snippet.title: Voidblazers | Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Out now on Playdate Catalog! https://play.date/games/voidblazers

Fasten your seatbelts, prepare to engage thrusters, and launch into an action-packed space adventure with Voidblazers!

Voidblazers is a story-driven shoot 'em up game for Playdate. Join the crew of Icarus as they travel across the galaxy, battle various fleets, and encounter new friends and enemies on their daring mission. 🚀
